<process draft="false" dev-studio-version="7.6.02.04">
  <process-def name=":AO-AD-Infoblox-NIOS:Find Items">
    <parameters>
      <input global="false" required="false">
        <description>The name of the adapter to use to handle the request. 
Default adapter name: InfobloxNIOS.</description>
        <from>adapter name</from>
        <to>adapter name</to>
      </input>
      <input global="false" required="true">
        <description>item type :
Defines the type of operation to be performed.

Supported 'item type'-
1. retrieve-network
2. retrieve-addresses
3. retrieve-dns-record
4. retrieve-fixed-address</description>
        <from>item type</from>
        <to>item type</to>
      </input>
      <input global="false" required="true">
        <description>The 'items' xml of the entity to be created.

1. Below is an example 'items' xml to find a Network

&lt;items&gt;
	&lt;item&gt;
		&lt;target&gt;
			&lt;host&gt;localhost&lt;/host&gt;
			&lt;user-name&gt;admin&lt;/user-name&gt;
			&lt;password encryption-type="Plain"&gt;test&lt;/password&gt;
			&lt;timeout-secs&gt;120&lt;/timeout-secs&gt;
		&lt;/target&gt;
		&lt;parameters&gt;
			&lt;network&gt;10.0.0.0&lt;/network&gt;
			&lt;mask&gt;24&lt;/mask&gt;
			&lt;comment&gt;Sample Comment&lt;/comment&gt;
			&lt;network-container&gt;10.0.0.0&lt;/network-container&gt;
			&lt;network-view&gt;default&lt;/network-view&gt;
			&lt;contains-address&gt;10.0.0.0&lt;/contains-address&gt;
			&lt;extensible-attributes&gt;
				&lt;attribute&gt;
					&lt;key&gt;Building&lt;/key&gt;
					&lt;value&gt;sample&lt;/value&gt;
				&lt;/attribute&gt;
			&lt;/extensible-attributes&gt;
		&lt;/parameters&gt;
&lt;/items&gt;

2. Below is an example 'items' xml to find a Fixed Address

Sample items Xml: 

1&gt; For IPV4
&lt;items&gt;
	&lt;item&gt;
		&lt;target&gt;
			&lt;host&gt;localhost&lt;/host&gt;
			&lt;user-name&gt;admin&lt;/user-name&gt;
			&lt;password encryption-type="Base64"&gt;YWRtaW4=&lt;/password&gt;
			&lt;timeout-secs&gt;120&lt;/timeout-secs&gt;
		&lt;/target&gt;
           &lt;parameters&gt;
			&lt;network&gt;10.0.0.0&lt;/network&gt;	
			&lt;mask&gt;24&lt;/mask&gt;
			&lt;network-view&gt;default&lt;/network-view&gt;
			&lt;network-type&gt;ipv4&lt;/network-type&gt;
			&lt;ip-address&gt;10.0.0.1&lt;/ip-address&gt;
			&lt;mac-address&gt;00:00:00:11:11:11&lt;/mac-address&gt;
			&lt;dhcp-client-identifier&gt;Value of dhcp-client-identifier&lt;/dhcp-client-identifier&gt;
			&lt;extensible-attributes&gt;
				&lt;attribute&gt;
					&lt;key&gt;Building&lt;/key&gt;
					&lt;value&gt;sample&lt;/value&gt;
				&lt;/attribute&gt;
			&lt;/extensible-attributes&gt;
           &lt;/parameters&gt;
      &lt;/item&gt;
&lt;/items&gt;

2&gt; For IPV6
&lt;items&gt;
	&lt;item&gt;
		&lt;target&gt;
			&lt;host&gt;localhost&lt;/host&gt;
			&lt;user-name&gt;admin&lt;/user-name&gt;
			&lt;password encryption-type="Base64"&gt;YWRtaW4=&lt;/password&gt;
			&lt;timeout-secs&gt;120&lt;/timeout-secs&gt;
		&lt;/target&gt;
           &lt;parameters&gt;
			&lt;network&gt;2002::&lt;/network&gt;	
			&lt;mask&gt;64&lt;/mask&gt;
			&lt;network-view&gt;default&lt;/network-view&gt;
			&lt;network-type&gt;ipv6&lt;/network-type&gt;
			&lt;ip-address&gt;2002::6&lt;/ip-address&gt;
			&lt;duid&gt;55:55&lt;/duid&gt;
			&lt;comment&gt;Value Of Comment&lt;/comment&gt;
			&lt;extensible-attributes&gt;
				&lt;attribute&gt;
					&lt;key&gt;Building&lt;/key&gt;
					&lt;value&gt;sample&lt;/value&gt;
				&lt;/attribute&gt;
			&lt;/extensible-attributes&gt;
           &lt;/parameters&gt;
      &lt;/item&gt;
&lt;/items&gt;</description>
